<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-3972] HintedHandoff fails to deliver any hints</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3972</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Summary says it all.  Whether in a memtable or sstable, no hints are delivered.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12544412">CASSANDRA-3972</key>
            <summary>HintedHandoff fails to deliver any hints</summary>
